               <p>THOMAS LEWIS. I live in <placeName id="t18260622-119-crimeloc591">Sidney-street, Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18260622-119-crimeloc591" type="placeName" value="Sidney-street, Islington"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18260622-119-crimeloc591" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18260622-119-off589 t18260622-119-crimeloc591"></join>. - The prisoner was in my employ for many years; I had a watch on my kitchen-dresser - he and I went through the kitchen; I then sent him out with a basket, and soon afterwards I missed the watch; next morning I went down to his house - he was in bed, but did not come down to me; I gave charge of him when he came to work - the duplicate was found in his box.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18260622-119-person734">
